<br><br>

In the Customer Card, Shipping tab the field "Periodic Tour Code" contains the table for the definition of periodic routes.
<br>

The data are entered in the Customers, Vendors, Ship to Addresses, Order Addresses master data. You can use this information as a filter for selecting documents in delivery routes.

<br>
